    <item>
      <title>司法部报告称特朗普可能因选举案被定罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/us-releasing-special-counsel-report-on-trump-2020-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特别顾问杰克·史密斯在向美国司法部提交的一份报告中表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普可能会因试图推翻 2020 年总统大选结果而被定罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/us-releasing-special-counsel-report-on-trump-2020-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 06:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲将努力团结起来抵制特朗普的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/europe-will-struggle-to-stand-united-against-trump-s-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲大陆的许多领导人在国内承受着巨大的压力，以至于他们不具备在全球事务上采取果断行动的政治影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/europe-will-struggle-to-stand-united-against-trump-s-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟科技主管称波罗的海电缆受损并非意外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/baltic-sea-cables-damage-can-t-be-accident-eu-tech-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟新任数字事务负责人汉娜·维克库宁 (Henna Virkkunen) 表示，波罗的海海底电缆屡屡遭到破坏不可能完全是意外，而该地区领导人正准备参加专门讨论该问题的北约峰会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/baltic-sea-cables-damage-can-t-be-accident-eu-tech-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理的重要政策演讲：值得关注的点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/france-pm-francois-bayrou-to-unveil-policies-in-bid-to-end-budget-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁将于周二向议员发表一次重要的政策演讲，以争取继续执政并确保制定紧急修复国家摇摇欲坠的公共财政的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/france-pm-francois-bayrou-to-unveil-policies-in-bid-to-end-budget-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲越来越乐观地认为特朗普不会放弃乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/europe-grows-more-optimistic-trump-won-t-abandon-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的欧洲盟友谨慎乐观地认为，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普不会强迫基辅与俄罗斯进行过早谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/europe-grows-more-optimistic-trump-won-t-abandon-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯的英国愿景因市场衰退面临新的危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/reeves-vision-for-britain-faces-fresh-peril-from-market-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 将于周二在英国遭遇市场动荡以来首次在议会发表讲话，这是本周工党领导层面临的几个潜在爆发点之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/reeves-vision-for-britain-faces-fresh-peril-from-market-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾要求中国撤回靠近岸边的“怪物”船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/philippines-tells-china-to-withdraw-monster-ship-nearing-shore</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾对一艘大型中国船只靠近其西海岸南海水域发出警报，这凸显了美国总统当选人唐纳德·特朗普就职前夕出现的新的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/philippines-tells-china-to-withdraw-monster-ship-nearing-shore</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国休庭决定尹某命运的首日审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/south-korea-to-begin-impeachment-trial-to-decide-on-yoon-s-fate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国于周二开始审理此案，随后休庭，以决定总统尹锡烈是否因其失败的戒严宣言而被永久免职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/south-korea-to-begin-impeachment-trial-to-decide-on-yoon-s-fate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和拜登称以色列和哈马斯即将达成加沙停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sullivan-cites-distinct-possibility-of-gaza-deal-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和乔·拜登都表示，他们乐观地认为以色列和哈马斯可以在几天内达成停火协议，从而暂停持续 15 个多月的加沙毁灭性战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sullivan-cites-distinct-possibility-of-gaza-deal-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
